                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8587" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1327</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2668 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻资产“增重”之路——亚洲渔港并购整合中联食品</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The road to asset-light &quot;weight gain&quot;——Asiasea M&amp;A China Link Food</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">姚宏，陈醉，刘丽丽（亚洲渔港股份有限公司），王娅，张洁如，褚师畅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">亚洲渔港股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资产重组与运营；并购动因；并购整合；协同效应；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Asset reorganization and operations; Acquisition motives; Integration; Synergistic effect</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从一家以海鲜餐饮解决方案为主的供应商，到如今有强大产业支撑的水产餐饮食材供应链龙头企业，亚洲渔港在轻资产的模式下飞速发展。但行业形势风云变幻，食品安全越来越受到关注，各路竞争对手也不断崛起，在新的行业竞争环境下亚洲渔港需要在研发、生产、供应链源头全面提升产业能力。在此背景下，创始人姜晓决定为亚洲渔港“增重”，并展开了与中联食品4年的坎坷谈判，终于在2020年底的疫情以及中美贸易战等复杂环境中迅速完成并购。并购后，亚洲渔港在多方面对中联食品展开整合，取长补短，最终实现并购整合的协同效应。本案例通过细致刻画展现亚洲渔港与中联食品从谈判到顺利并购、完成整合的全部决策过程，帮助学员掌握轻资产企业通过并购的“主动增重路径”，理解并购动因、并购时机选择、并购风险、并购整合等理论知识，为中国水产行业中的传统企业，如何通过资产重组与运营，健身塑体，不断瞄准产业链价值高地，提高产业综合制造与服务能力，冲击国际行业市场提供参考和借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With an asset-light 	strategy, Asiasea has developed from a small trading company to today&#39;s leading food supply chain enterprises. However, with increasing attention on food safety problem and the rise of competitors, the industry situation is changing. In the new competitive environment of the industry, Asiasea needs to improve industrial capacity across the board in R&amp;D, production, and supply chain sources. Against this backdrop, General Manager Jiang Xiao decided to &quot;add weight&quot; to Asiasea, trying to M&amp;A China Link Food and embarking on a bumpy 4-year negotiation process, which finally got completed at the end of 2020 amidst the complex environment of the COVID-19. After the completion of the M&amp;A, Asiasea integrated China Link Food from various aspects in early 2021, fully complementing its strengths and weaknesses, and finally realizing the synergies of the merger and integration. This case shows all the decision-making process of Asiasea and China Link Food from negotiation to smooth merger and acquisition and completion of integration through detailed drawing, which helps participants to grasp the “active weight gain path” of asset-light enterprises through M&amp;A, and to understand the theoretical knowledge such as M&amp;A motivation, M&amp;A timing, M&amp;A risk, M&amp;A integration and so on. Moreover, it provides references and reference for the traditional enterprises of China&#39;s aquaculture industry to know how they can aim at the highland of the industrial chain value by means of asset reorganization and operation, fitness molding and improve the industry&#39;s comprehensive manufacturing and service capability and impact on the international industry market.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购》、《企业并购与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购动因理论；SOR理论；并购风险理论；并购协同效应理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
